I bumped into someone today.

11
00:01:53,970 --> 00:01:55,630
Are you interested to know...

12
00:01:56,320 --> 00:01:57,370
Wu, calm down.

13
00:01:57,830 --> 00:01:58,840
I can't.

14
00:01:59,090 --> 00:02:00,550
Either you kill her today,

15
00:02:00,560 --> 00:02:01,910
or I'll die right here!

16
