You don't deserve to be a police officer!

17
00:02:11,990 --> 00:02:12,910
Let her go.

18
00:02:15,810 --> 00:02:16,570
Wu.

19
00:02:17,950 --> 00:02:18,829
I understand

20
00:02:18,829 --> 00:02:20,390
how you're feeling now.

21
00:02:20,850 --> 00:02:22,700
But according to the law,

22
00:02:23,030 --> 00:02:24,800
we have no way

23
00:02:25,340 --> 00:02:26,230
of taking your younger brother's murderer

24
00:02:26,230 --> 00:02:27,700
to the final trial now.

25
00:02:28,120 --> 00:02:29,040
I've told you

26
00:02:29,040 --> 00:02:29,710
the reasons

27
00:02:29,710 --> 00:02:31,140
many times.

28
00:02:31,730 --> 00:02:32,400
I know

29
00:02:32,610 --> 00:02:34,290
we made you wait too long.

30
00:02:34,790 --> 00:02:35,550
But

31
00:02:36,520 --> 00:02:37,720
please rest assured,

32
00:02:38,200 --> 00:02:39,250
we won't let

33
00:02:39,960 --> 00:02:41,890
this trial drag on indefinitely.

34
00:02:43,570 --> 00:02:44,870
Trust me this once,

35
00:02:45,670 --> 00:02:46,340
okay?

36
00:02:50,710 --> 00:02:52,310
It was a case I handled

37
00:02:52,310 --> 00:02:54,410
when I was in the Chengnan Sub-Bureau.

38
00:02:54,410 --> 00:02:56,340
It was a marriage fraud and murder.

39
00:02:57,470 --> 00:02:58,980
From the first case

40
00:02:59,240 --> 00:03:00,410
in 2013,

41
00:03:00,830 --> 00:03:01,970
until 2014

42
00:03:01,970 --> 00:03:03,670
when the suspect was arrested.

43
00:03:03,670 --> 00:03:05,030
She has committed the crime thrice

44
00:03:05,030 --> 00:03:06,250
with four victims.

45
00:03:07,890 --> 00:03:09,480
I've heard of this case.

46
00:03:09,820 --> 00:03:11,160
The suspect is a woman.

47
00:03:12,550 --> 00:03:13,010
But I thought

48
00:03:13,010 --> 00:03:14,060
she was sentenced to death

49
00:03:14,060 --> 00:03:15,490
in 2015.

50
00:03:16,120 --> 00:03:18,579
It was the death sentence in the first trial.

51
00:03:18,600 --> 00:03:19,770
But she changed her statement

52
00:03:19,770 --> 00:03:20,910
in the second trial.

53
00:03:21,710 --> 00:03:22,920
She claimed her accomplice forced her

54
00:03:22,920 --> 00:03:24,560
to commit the crime.

55
00:03:25,280 --> 00:03:26,960
We can't verify

56
00:03:27,210 --> 00:03:28,640
if anyone did force her

57
00:03:28,930 --> 00:03:29,350
because we haven't found

58
00:03:29,350 --> 00:03:30,820
this person until now.

59
00:03:31,740 --> 00:03:33,070
That's why we have no way

60
00:03:33,130 --> 00:03:34,310
of transferring this case

61
00:03:34,310 --> 00:03:35,610
to the procuratorate.

62
00:03:35,820 --> 00:03:38,480
No wonder the victim's family made a scene here.

63
00:03:39,810 --> 00:03:40,980
Didn't anyone come up with a composite drawing

64
00:03:40,980 --> 00:03:42,410
of her accomplice?

65
00:03:43,079 --> 00:03:45,140
The suspect provided the descriptions several times.

66
00:03:45,140 --> 00:03:46,400
The composite drawings were sketched

67
00:03:46,400 --> 00:03:48,079
by forensic artists of different sub-bureaus,

68
00:03:48,079 --> 00:03:50,010
but each sketch looked different.

69
00:03:50,520 --> 00:03:51,740
So this is the hardest part

70
00:03:51,740 --> 00:03:52,700
of this case.

71
00:03:52,910 --> 00:03:54,050
The suspect clearly wants

72
00:03:54,050 --> 00:03:56,020
to delay the hearing.

73
00:03:58,450 --> 00:03:59,579
Bureau Chief Zhang,

74
00:03:59,670 --> 00:04:00,810
